data.description: Welcome to Frangista Beach! This spacious and stunning newly built beach house features both modern amenities and architectural character in a fantastic gated beach community w/ PRIVATE/DEEDED beach access. Sold Fully furnished, turn key ready and a rental machine. This home boasts an open living concept. The gorgeous oversized kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, large island, custom backsplash + more. 3 Bedroom + custom built Hallway Bunk area . Backyard showcases a covered porch, nature views + lots of room for family vacation activities. Just steps away from the community pool and the World's most beautiful beaches.  An amazing beach house to call your full time residence, short term vacation home or 2nd home The Villas of Frangista is a quiet, gated community with beautiful cobble stone streets, a community pool and quiet fishing ponds for kids to fish in. The gated community is just minutes from the sugar white sands, close to favorite local restaurants, and nearby some of the best shopping in the area. This one is truly a sight to see!
